column14:
1. As a customer, I can add username so that I can login
2. As a customer, I can  add password so that I can login
3. As a customer, I can  add full name so that I am recognize by driver and make reservation
4. As a customer, I can  add contact number so that I can be contacted by driver and staff
5. As a customer, I can  add email address so that i can receive the latest news and promotion
6. As a customer, I can  add date of birth so that staff can send me birthday wishes and birthday promotion or voucher.
